{"type": "article", "id": 28131, "title": "DIY 烛台", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-14T06:41:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702143946tDxOr4YdNGzEfkgR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>还记得我们之前介绍过的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27921.html\">可以拉伸的烛台</a>吗？今天介绍的 Folding Tea 同样是一个让你能够 DIY 的烛台，是 Pilsoo Han 为韩国 <a href=\"http://thisissoftpaper.com/\">Softpaper</a> 工作室设计的作品。它采用柔性钢制成，上面刻有垂直的缝隙，沿着它们慢慢折叠就能构成漂亮的几何形容器。一侧还设计了一个小钢片，不仅起到了两边相连的作用，还能用作烛台的手柄。目前它还处于量产阶段，可以通过<a href=\"http://thisissoftpaper.com/?page_id=16108\">链接</a>联系工作室购买。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439448Ddxsai5MIUFmNJ9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143945qC2rhsUvEL0ANJay.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021439450NV7IOFUX3n1B2HY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66870416\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702143945CQB57x1FbA8qV6rg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}